      <title>中国电动汽车价格战即将结束吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-30/is-an-end-to-china-s-ev-price-war-finally-in-sight-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰前海证券中国汽车研究部主管丁玉倩表示，她预计中国电动汽车行业新车型的供应将从 9 月开始回升，并有助于缓解持续的价格战。她与 Yvonne Man 和 David Ingles 在“彭博：中国秀”中讨论了她在财报季的主要收获。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-30/is-an-end-to-china-s-ev-price-war-finally-in-sight-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 05:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
